  <brief_title>Somatostatin, Octreotide, Pentoxyfilline in the Prevention of Post-ERCP Pancreatitis and Molecular Markers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Octreotide, Somatostatin, Pentoxyfilline or Placebo in the Prevention and the Course of Post-ERCP Pancreatitis and Study of Molecular Markers in Post-ERCP Pancreatitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
